				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The main point is that you have two audiences with different needs. Emulator authors need to know every detail. Duplicating information in this detailed description is a violation of the DRY principle, and leads to inconsistencies. Programmers generally only need to know how to make the desired sounds, so a different format is called for. The new page hopefully serves many programmers.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

