				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Here's a big APU gotcha:  Even if you're not using the sweep unit, you must still write 0x08 to the sweep register, otherwise it won't play the lowest notes.
<br />
<br />There are features in the APU that stop a note when the current period + "whatever sweep would add" becomes too high, and writing that value to the sweep register stops that.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Here come the fortune cookies!  Here come the fortune cookies!  They're wearing paper hats!</div>
					
